Interface PropertyEditor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PropertyBooleanEditor, PropertyCameraEditor, PropertyChannelEditor, PropertyDoubleEditor, PropertyEditorAdapter, PropertyEnumEditor, PropertyFocusEditor, PropertyIntegerEditor, PropertyStringEditor

    public interface PropertyEditor
    Interface all editors for certain types of properties of a configuration implement.
